targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  "timestamp" AS "time",
  battery_percentage
FROM "vehicle-states"
WHERE
  vehicle = $vehicle

SELECT
  forecast_timestamp AS "time",
  forecasted_battery_percentage
FROM predicted_battery
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(forecast_timestamp) AND
  vehicle = '$vehicle'
ORDER BY 1
